doc.after: The airline was established on 20 July 1989 trading with the name Zagal formally Zagreb Airlines and started operations using a single Cessna 402 aircraft on cargo services for UPS After the first democratic elections held in Croatia Zagal changed its name to Croatia Airlines 3 on 23 July 1990
